      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  StreamManagementIOProcessor.Counter
      Counter class implements proper counter with overflow from 2^32-1 to 0
      static class  StreamManagementIOProcessor.OutQueue
      OutQueue class implements queue of outgoing packets waiting for ack with implementation of removing acked elements when id of acked packet is passed

      • shouldRequestAck

        protected boolean shouldRequestAck(XMPPIOService service,
                                   StreamManagementIOProcessor.OutQueue outQueue)
        Override this method to define a custom behaviour for request ack. The default implementation will request an ack if there are more than ack_request_count packets waiting, so you probably want to OR your behaviour with this.
